{"id": "1479395758225756259", "channel_id": "1479210453295955988", "type": 19, "author_id": "1131790839291596841", "author_name": "morimensstaff01", "author_bot": false, "content": "I'll check this suggestion again later, as I'm currently preparing content for a new version.<:camera:1356053040251146460>", "timestamp": "2026-03-06T08:30:34.605000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": ["1160510535670968330"], "reactions": [{"emoji": "❤️", "emoji_id": null, "count": 5}], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": "1479392645871566968", "has_thread": false, "thread_id": null, "flags": 0}
{"id": "1479417058209959976", "channel_id": "1479210453295955988", "type": 0, "author_id": "1131790839291596841", "author_name": "morimensstaff01", "author_bot": false, "content": "To avoid misunderstanding, I've summarized the content of this post into the following two suggestions (I'm not sure if my understanding is correct):\n\nThe Tentacle Gathering effect of Returnal Line increases attack times, and currently there are no Covenants that can help increase the number of tentacles. Perhaps some new sets are needed?\n\nA certain number of \"temporary tentacles\" or \"tentacle gatherings\" can be converted into permanent tentacles. Is the intention to provide more ways to obtain permanent tentacles?", "timestamp": "2026-03-06T09:55:12.917000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": null, "flags": 0}
{"id": "1479418305335787593", "channel_id": "1479210453295955988", "type": 19, "author_id": "452516689225973761", "author_name": "thpdom", "author_bot": false, "content": "It's more that returnal line could use a rework, since it was never a useful covenant.", "timestamp": "2026-03-06T10:00:10.255000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": ["1131790839291596841"], "reactions": [{"emoji": "cry3", "emoji_id": "1356082134447558748", "count": 1}], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": "1479417058209959976", "has_thread": false, "thread_id": null, "flags": 0}
{"id": "1479418317562187909", "channel_id": "1479210453295955988", "type": 0, "author_id": "452516689225973761", "author_name": "thpdom", "author_bot": false, "content": "<:takenotes:1357186646294138890>", "timestamp": "2026-03-06T10:00:13.170000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": null, "flags": 0}
{"id": "1479422473551347806", "channel_id": "1479210453295955988", "type": 19, "author_id": "1131790839291596841", "author_name": "morimensstaff01", "author_bot": false, "content": "This means that the tentacles want numbers more than attack times.", "timestamp": "2026-03-06T10:16:44.035000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": ["452516689225973761"], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": "1479418305335787593", "has_thread": false, "thread_id": null, "flags": 0}
{"id": "1479424650621620235", "channel_id": "1479210453295955988", "type": 19, "author_id": "452516689225973761", "author_name": "thpdom", "author_bot": false, "content": "It's an interesting dillema. Since to get 2 attack times per turn almost consistently you need around 300 team RM(realm mastery). Building that takes away from other members stat capabilities, In general reduces tentacle damage because you sacrifice some damage amp. And only yields... 2 more hits. As it stands It either needs to give more hits, or do something completely different.\n\nWhether those numbers get made back via tentacle stance RM scaling is something i don't know. But it still makes the covenant currently an outright downgrade to any team.", "timestamp": "2026-03-06T10:25:23.089000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": "2026-03-06T10:25:41.822000+00:00", "pinned": false, "mentions": ["1131790839291596841"], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": "1479422473551347806", "has_thread": false, "thread_id": null, "flags": 0}
{"id": "1479425683787874385", "channel_id": "1479210453295955988", "type": 19, "author_id": "1437487264023318668", "author_name": "vxvendetta97", "author_bot": false, "content": "yeah, i think the point is mostly that the effect itself, in the current state and scaling, is too underwhelming to find real use in a team.\nSo either a complete or partial rework or a big increase in the scaling (maybe with a cap to not make it too high) could be options.", "timestamp": "2026-03-06T10:29:29.415000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": ["1131790839291596841"], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": "1479417058209959976", "has_thread": false, "thread_id": null, "flags": 0}
{"id": "1479425956467970211", "channel_id": "1479210453295955988", "type": 0, "author_id": "452516689225973761", "author_name": "thpdom", "author_bot": false, "content": "It would need a cap yeah. Because with it working with divine realm some of the strongest Gmurphy comps would become even stronger, i'm pretty sure.", "timestamp": "2026-03-06T10:30:34.427000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": null, "flags": 0}
{"id": "1479426054765678783", "channel_id": "1479210453295955988", "type": 0, "author_id": "1437487264023318668", "author_name": "vxvendetta97", "author_bot": false, "content": "honestly making it a cov that help you build tentacles faster could be a very interesting direction to help pure tentacles teams and mixed realm teams", "timestamp": "2026-03-06T10:30:57.863000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": "2026-03-06T10:31:16.781000+00:00", "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [{"emoji": "agree", "emoji_id": "1400771815076528258", "count": 4}], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": null, "flags": 0}
{"id": "1479426382617378918", "channel_id": "1479210453295955988", "type": 0, "author_id": "452516689225973761", "author_name": "thpdom", "author_bot": false, "content": "I don't hate the concept of more hits as well, any of the 2 ideas could be a new covenant. Because more hits would give the old tentacle damage teams, Like aeqour Clem some staying power.", "timestamp": "2026-03-06T10:32:16.029000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": "2026-03-06T10:32:25.941000+00:00", "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": null, "flags": 0}
{"id": "1479426781554409565", "channel_id": "1479210453295955988", "type": 0, "author_id": "452516689225973761", "author_name": "thpdom", "author_bot": false, "content": "If we drop the hits, it could also increase how much strength scales tentacles based on RM. \nThat's actually a really good idea. like a +25% strength tentacle scaling based on RM.", "timestamp": "2026-03-06T10:33:51.143000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": "2026-03-06T10:53:30.092000+00:00", "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": null, "flags": 0}
